description: Chef Daniel is doing a great service to the city of Denver, with this astounding crepe cart.Crepe Gatsby brings the sweet and savory joy of these French delicacies to the Mile High City. Whether you're after their Sweet Nutella or London Broil Roast Beef we just know you'll leave this food cart happy and satisfied.Experience the unique sensation your taste buds will come to crave, grab one of these great Gatsby crepes today!
name: Crepe Gatsby
